sourceDescription: This database is a searchable, digitized version of the indices of civil registrations in England and Wales, reported quarterly to the General Register Office (GRO) in London. This index spans the years between 1916 and 2007. You need the information found in an original index to request a copy of a birth certificate for the individual referenced. Learn more...
